1
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:44,680
Could you close the window? It's a bit cold.

2
00:00:57,800 --> 00:00:59,060
Where are we going now?

3
00:00:59,480 --> 00:00:59,760
We're here.

4
00:00:59,760 --> 00:01:01,560
Don't tell me I'll know when we get there.

5
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:03,680
I don't care what your purpose or mission is.

6
00:01:03,680 --> 00:01:04,680
Save me if you want,

7
00:01:04,680 --> 00:01:05,880
or don't.

8
00:01:05,880 --> 00:01:08,080
I don't want to be your bargaining chip.

9
00:01:08,360 --> 00:01:10,840
This feeling of jumping from the frying pan into the fire

10
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:11,840
is really bad.

11
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,000
To Yuanzhou.

12
00:01:15,880 --> 00:01:19,280
There's a direct train to Europe tomorrow at 3:00 PM.

13
00:01:19,600 --> 00:01:21,600
Wouldn't it have been faster if we went straight

14
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:22,760
to the train station or airport earlier?

15
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:24,560
Didn't you say before

16
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:26,480
that they have resources and brains?

17
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:29,480
They must have heavily guarded those places already.

18
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:32,240
But with so many people at the train station and airport,

19
00:01:32,240 --> 00:01:33,240
in broad daylight,

20
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:34,479
could they just snatch me?

21
00:01:34,479 --> 00:01:36,360
They don't need to snatch you.

22
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:39,180
They just need to create some chaos to delay you.

23
00:01:39,479 --> 00:01:42,610
That way, they'll have time to manipulate other things.

24
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:45,320
Then why go to Yuanzhou?

25
00:01:45,640 --> 00:01:47,680
Other nearby cities have flights

26
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:49,280
and trains to Europe too.

27
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:52,160
Because I chose Yuanzhou randomly.

28
00:01:53,240 --> 00:01:54,880
If my own choices

29
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:56,240
lack logic,

30
00:01:56,479 --> 00:01:58,610
it'll be even harder for them to guess.

31
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:03,280
You're quite cautious.

32
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,760
So how long until we reach Yuanzhou?

33
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,120
Seven hours.

34
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:49,840
So you're Huzi.

35
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:51,880
Is Huzi a name you can call me?

36
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:27,520
Check

37
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:30,120
all the places where they might leave their ID records.

38
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:30,720
I did.

39
00:03:31,040 --> 00:03:33,960
That woman bought train, bus, and flight tickets at the same time.

40
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:36,440
I've already arranged people in these places

41
00:03:36,440 --> 00:03:37,440
to intercept them at any time.

42
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:38,320
No need.

43
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:40,079
She probably won't take that route.

44
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:42,880
I guess they've already left the city and are trying to go abroad.

45
00:03:42,880 --> 00:03:45,120
Keep tracking their ID usage records.

46
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:48,360
They'll need it whether they stay in a hotel or do anything else.

47
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:50,520
What if they don't use their IDs?

48
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:54,280
How would I know?

49
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:57,850
Swearing again.

50
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,400
Look up all the vehicles registered

51
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:08,480
under them and their friends.

52
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:09,840
Okay.

53
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:24,240
Get your brother

54
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:25,720
some fruit.

55
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,820
Tell them to be more polite in the future.

56
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:48,600
Are you sleepy?

57
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:50,060
Let's find a place to rest.

58
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:51,960
I'm fine. No need.

59
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,640
For our safety,

60
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:14,770
we must find a place to rest.

61
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,050
There's still time.

62
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:18,360
Let's find a place to park.

63
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,060
We can take a nap in the car.

64
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,320
In the car?

65
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:22,780
How can we rest?

66
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:23,800
No.

67
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,320
I want to stay in a hotel.

68
00:05:25,320 --> 00:05:27,680
We are on the run, lady.

69
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:29,200
And you want to stay in a hotel?

70
00:05:29,200 --> 00:05:31,130
They haven't caught up with us yet.

71
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,680
Your plan was so thorough.

72
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:37,920
They might be waiting for us at the train station or airport in Tangzhou.

73
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:42,360
Besides, a man and a woman alone in a car...

74
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:43,880
Who knows

75
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:47,440
what bad intentions you might have.

76
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:52,740
Do I look like that kind of person?

77
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:53,840
You do.

78
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:56,200
So be it.

79
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,580
You have no choice.

80
00:06:08,320 --> 00:06:08,960
What are you doing?

81
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:11,520
I am someone who demands a certain quality of life.

82
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:14,180
I can't sleep without changing into my pajamas.

83
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,600
Don't peek.

84
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,120
Hey, wake up.

85
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,010
I need to go to the bathroom.

86
00:06:58,920 --> 00:06:59,720
Go ahead.

87
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:02,380
It's cold outside. Can I borrow your jacket?

88
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:26,880
Jessica.

89
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:29,320
Jessica.

90
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:31,960
Jessica.

91
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,760
What took you so long?

92
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:45,680
How were you so sure I could find you?

93
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:48,120
Didn't I tell you?

94
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:50,960
I have high standards for my quality of life,

95
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:53,760
and this is the best hotel around here.

96
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:58,220
Where's the passport?

97
00:07:58,280 --> 00:07:59,400
I put it away.

98
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,440
Don't worry. I won't run.

99
00:08:09,960 --> 00:08:10,760
Hello?

100
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:12,320
I just found out.

101
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:14,580
They booked a room at a hotel in Songzhou.

102
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:17,520
Okay.

103
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,000
Send me the location.

104
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:40,360
Get me the new pajamas from my bag.

105
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,159
Thanks.

106
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:44,370
Didn't you go in wearing your pajamas?

107
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:46,440
That set got dirty in the car.

108
00:08:58,280 --> 00:08:58,920
Here.

109
00:09:15,920 --> 00:09:17,280
Why is your face red?

110
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:22,040
Because it's hot.

111
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:23,240
Why did you

112
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:24,840
turn the AC up so high?

113
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:26,840
Are you really that afraid of the cold?

114
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,320
My family was poor when I was little.

115
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,440
I was malnourished,

116
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,360
so I'm weak and sensitive to the cold.

117
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:32,490
You really can lie through your teeth.

118
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,680
Poor when you were little?

119
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:36,340
With your standard of living,

120
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:37,820
did you snag a sugar daddy?

121
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:40,200
Can't I rely on myself?

122
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:42,000
I am a computer engineer.

123
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:43,480
In high school,

124
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:46,800
I won the top prize in the Kaggle global big data competition.

125
00:09:46,800 --> 00:09:48,280
I became one of the top people in my age group

126
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:50,640
in the world of computer science.

127
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:52,200
Then why did you come to China?

128
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:52,880
For work.

129
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:55,520
Why was your passport held by a loan shark?

130
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,400
Don't ask about that.

131
00:09:58,800 --> 00:09:59,930
It's better for you.

132
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:01,530
Get some rest early.

133
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:03,100
It's getting late.

134
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:07,760
How are we going to sleep?

135
00:10:09,760 --> 00:10:11,960
You sleep on the bed. I'll take the sofa.

136
00:10:20,880 --> 00:10:22,680
The sofa must be uncomfortable.

137
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:25,800
It's fine.

138
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:26,560
Whatever.

139
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:29,320
Since we are alone in the same room,

140
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,970
we can't explain it anyway.

141
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:32,560
Come sleep on the bed.

142
00:10:32,920 --> 00:10:33,680
I trust you,

143
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:36,480
and you are my benefactor.

144
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:39,060
Even if you do something to me,

145
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,440
I won't resist.

146
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:42,370
I'll consider it repaying you.

147
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:45,760
It sounds like you want to give yourself to me.

148
00:10:45,920 --> 00:10:46,920
Sorry,

149
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:48,890
you might not be picky, but I am.

150
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:52,040
Are you really picky,

151
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,860
or are you just scared?

152
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:58,320
Or maybe you can't perform in that area?

153
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,280
What?

154
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:35,180
You are saying you're not coming now?

155
00:11:35,880 --> 00:11:37,680
I've already booked the room.

156
00:11:41,160 --> 00:11:42,890
Your husband is back, isn't he?

157
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:45,080
Fine.

158
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:47,400
Next time then.

159
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:50,680
What a pity.

160
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:53,520
Got stood up on such a beautiful night.

161
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:56,020
Some people want it but don't have it.

162
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,480
You have it

163
00:11:58,040 --> 00:11:59,440
but don't appreciate it,

164
00:11:59,760 --> 00:12:01,290
enjoying loneliness here.

165
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:03,560
Those who know

166
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:05,920
would say you have strong willpower.

167
00:12:05,920 --> 00:12:06,800
Those who don't

168
00:12:07,120 --> 00:12:08,920
might think I'm not attractive.

169
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:15,840
Do you want to try?

170
00:12:18,520 --> 00:12:19,720
I'm kidding.

171
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:20,620
I'm sleepy.

172
00:12:21,160 --> 00:12:21,890
Going to bed.

173
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:32,920
Hello.

174
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:35,740
My colleague booked a room at your hotel.

175
00:12:35,880 --> 00:12:37,720
But I can't reach him right now.

176
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:40,490
Could you check his room number for me?

177
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:42,080
You threw up everywhere.

178
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,810
Yet you're sleeping like a log.

179
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:45,160
All you do is drink all day.

180
00:12:45,160 --> 00:12:47,000
And you expect me to clean up after you?

181
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:48,800
Do you think you're a man-child?

182
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:50,760
Hurry up and clean this up.

183
00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:51,800
It stinks.

184
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:54,180
The smell is giving me a headache.

185
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:22,320
Your husband is back, right?

186
00:14:22,520 --> 00:14:23,600
All right.

187
00:14:25,400 --> 00:14:26,400
I'm just kidding.

188
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:27,380
I'm sleepy.

189
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:29,600
Wait a minute.

190
00:14:30,520 --> 00:14:31,580
I'm from next door.

191
00:14:31,920 --> 00:14:35,040
I heard you on the phone saying the person you're meeting can't make it.

192
00:14:35,040 --> 00:14:36,680
My girlfriend and I just had a fight.

193
00:14:36,680 --> 00:14:38,080
We want to sleep separately.

194
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:40,210
How about you transfer this room to me?

195
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:01,240
Hello.

196
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:03,490
I've lost it for now.

197
00:15:04,400 --> 00:15:06,400
But I'll find it as soon as possible.

198
00:15:26,680 --> 00:15:27,480
Time to go.

199
00:16:10,560 --> 00:16:11,680
Tang 678N1.

200
00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:14,120
Check the owner's information.

201
00:16:23,040 --> 00:16:23,800
Hey, baby.

202
00:16:24,360 --> 00:16:25,420
What are you doing?

203
00:16:26,680 --> 00:16:28,440
I'm working overtime today.

204
00:16:28,680 --> 00:16:29,480
Don't worry.

205
00:16:29,680 --> 00:16:33,140
I'll definitely go back to keep you company when I'm done here.

206
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:34,360
Don't worry.

207
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:36,900
I'll definitely have time tomorrow.

208
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:57,240
Sorry, man.

209
00:16:57,520 --> 00:16:58,920
I'm in a bad mood.

210
00:17:11,760 --> 00:17:13,359
I found the info on the car.
